{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XAv9H2EkjgXTPrSihaajxq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. The transform statefulset needs:\n1. The `es-transform-config` configmap (which doesn't exist - this is the \"capacity change\" that broke things)\n2. Cert mounts for TLS (which are missing from the statefulset)\n\nMy plan:\n1. Create the `es-transform-config` configmap with transform node config including TLS settings\n2. Patch the `es-transform` statefulset to add cert mounts from `es-http-tls` secret\n3. Scale the statefulset to 1\n4. Wait for the transform node to join the cluster\n5. Create the `events-by-service` transform and start it\n\nThe tricky part is transport TLS - the transform node needs to use the same CA-signed certificates from the `es-http-tls` secret to communicate with the data nodes, since they all require transport SSL verification.\n\nLooking at the original statefulset configuration, it seems the transform node was deployed without certificate mounts initially, which wouldn't work if the cluster enforces transport TLS. I need to patch the statefulset to add the cert mounts and update the config to reference them, then scale it up. The transform role isn't included by default in ES 7.17, so I need to create the configmap with the proper role configuration and TLS settings that match the existing cluster setup. Then I'll patch the statefulset to mount the certificates, scale it up to one replica, and once the node joins, create and start the transform job to process the events data. I'm also realizing the transport layer uses the same certificates as HTTP, so I need to make sure both are properly configured.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4176,"cache_read_input_tokens":44338,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4176},"output_tokens":20,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"afd55ec6-6f6c-43e2-bca3-7c11c76505cd","uuid":"d230695e-2248-48b8-a813-457fa4febeab","request_id":"req_011Cc9gpNdbXuKfHpW9fWtfr"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XAv9H2EkjgXTPrSihaajxq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `es-transform-config` configmap is missing (deleted as part of the scenario), and the statefulset lacks cert mounts needed for TLS. I'll restore both, then scale up the transform node and create/start the transform.\n\n**Step 1: Create the missing `es-transform-config` configmap:**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4176,"cache_read_input_tokens":44338,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4176},"output_tokens":20,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"afd55ec6-6f6c-43e2-bca3-7c11c76505cd","uuid":"567db2f2-a74a-43f4-b0cf-013e8d794321","request_id":"req_011Cc9gpNdbXuKfHpW9fWtfr"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XAv9H2EkjgXTPrSihaajxq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0187UZ9JY36aQNhmdW2az9Xz","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl -n elasticsearch create configmap es-transform-config --from-literal=elasticsearch.yml='cluster.name: es-cluster\nnode.name: ${POD_NAME}\nnode.roles: [ transform ]\nnetwork.host: 0.0.0.0\n\ndiscovery.seed_hosts:\n  - es-cluster-0.es-cluster.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local\n  - es-cluster-1.es-cluster.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local\n  - es-cluster-2.es-cluster.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local\n\nnode.store.allow_mmap: false\n\nxpack.security.enabled: true\nxpack.security.autoconfiguration.enabled: false\n\nxpack.security.http.ssl.enabled: true\nxpack.security.http.ssl.key: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.key\nxpack.security.http.ssl.certificate: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.crt\nxpack.security.http.ssl.certificate_authorities: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/ca.crt\nxpack.security.http.ssl.verification_mode: certificate\n\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.enabled: true\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.verification_mode: certificate\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.key: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.key\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.certificate: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.crt\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.certificate_authorities: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/ca.crt\n' 2>&1","description":"Create es-transform-config configmap"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4176,"cache_read_input_tokens":44338,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4176},"output_tokens":20,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"afd55ec6-6f6c-43e2-bca3-7c11c76